請說明該家禽產業之供應鏈業者可採取那些協力合作的策略？（8分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9647c515050c", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "319", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "農業經濟學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "農業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
